[Course_Description]
Construction drawings can come in many shapes, sizes, and formats, but the industry is moving toward a paperless environment. To keep up, you need to take your entire document management process digital. Bluebeam Revu is a great choice, offering a central location to create, edit, and store digital drawings, and sharing and collaboration features that ensure changes and comments are always tracked and saved. It's software designed for AEC professionals, by AEC professionals. This course will make sure you get the most out of Bluebeam's advanced organization, markup, and navigation features, so you can easily manage and share documents within construction teams.